al-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117804/apple-watch-series-9-sennheiser-momentum-true-wireless-3-earbuds-fujifilm-instax-mini-12-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117804/apple-watch-series-9-sennheiser-momentum-true-wireless-3-earbuds-fujifilm-instax-mini-12-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T11:32:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T11:32:15-04:00</updated><title>以下是您现在可以获得的最佳 AirPods 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;打开充电盒中的一对 AirPods&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wgRHHy2tVrdpKQeZ6AJ-8DNmQ6Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67012056/226285_AIRPODS_PRO_2_cwelch_0012.35.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;配备 USB-C 的第二代 AirPods Pro 在亚马逊的起价为 199 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NjCYhY&quot;>;如果您知道去哪里寻找，您通常可以在苹果广受欢迎的 AirPods 上获得折扣。自从 Apple 推出 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/10/18/22671344/apple-new-airpods-3-spacial-audio-specs-price-release-date-features&quot;>;到 2021 年底第三代 AirPods&lt;/a>; 推出后，我们看到第二代入门级型号的起价慢慢降至 100 美元以下。现在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23878402/apple-airpods-pro-usb-c-adaptive-audio-conversation-awareness-test-review&quot;>;最新的AirPods Pro&lt;/a >; 已经上市一年多了，我们也看到它们的价格下跌得更频繁。我们甚至看到更新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23878402/apple-airpods-pro-usb-c-adaptive-audio-conversation-awareness-test-review 上有很多优惠&quot;>;配备 USB-C 的 AirPods Pro&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;0BxYYe&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component= &quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple WWDC 2024 定于 6 月 10 日举行&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /3/26/24111331/apple-wwdc-2024-event-date-ai-artificial-intelligence-m4-ios-18&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;苹果的可穿戴创意包括智能眼镜和耳朵里的摄像头&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/25/24082760/apple-smart-glasses-airpods-cameras-smart-ring&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;美国诉苹果：你需要知道的一切&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24107581/doj-v-apple-antitrust-monoply-news-updates&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;E6INSh&quot;>;在这里，我们精选了各型号目前最优惠的价格，包括入门级 AirPods、AirPods Pro、第三代 AirPods 和 AirPods Max。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;Hh97yA&quot;>; &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://s3.amazonaws.com/assets.sbnation.com/csk/uploads/verge-toc.css&quot;>; &lt; div class=&quot;duet--article--article-body-component verge-table-of-contents border-franklin border&quot; id=&quot;toc-main&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;ej2msf&quot; >;最佳 AirPods（第二代）优惠&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;upOxaE&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:9502973&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;layout&quot;:&quot; full_with_square_img&quot;}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;eg29V6&quot;>;2021 年，Apple 降低了第二代 AirPods 的定价 - 现在是...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T11:11:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T11:11:54-04:00</updated><title>如何将您的主题帖子交叉发布到 fediverse</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;矢量拼贴画显示使用线程的各个方面。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Unbld2im6lM8P35CAiQin3fjBwI=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246878/HT055_THREADS_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;KeBFdu&quot;>;看起来联邦宇宙正在开放。 3 月底，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107881/threads-fediverse-beta-launch-mastodon&quot;>;Meta 的 Threads 推出了一项测试版功能&lt;/a>;，该功能允许来自美国、加拿大或日本的用户可以交叉发布并查看 Mastodon 以及其他联合社交网络的点赞。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;rhvH3V&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Threads 的 fediverse 测试版开放，分享您在 Mastodon 上的帖子，太&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107881/threads-fediverse-beta-launch-mastodon&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;JdCY4Y&quot;>;如果您是来自这三个国家之一的 Threads 用户，并且想尝试一下此测试版，那么这并不困难。您可以通过移动应用程序或网络版本执行此操作：&lt;/p>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;JYi24z&quot;>;在 Threads 的移动应用程序中，点击右下角的&lt;strong>;个人资料图标&lt;/strong>; ，点击右上角的两行，然后选择&lt;strong>;帐户>; Fediverse 分享&lt;/strong>;。&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;eGAtUd&quot;>;在网页版上，点击右上角的两行，然后选择&lt;strong>;设置 >;帐户选项卡 >; Fediverse 共享&lt;/strong>;。&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;在...中查找 Fediverse 共享选项&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt; /figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T10:15:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T10:15:00-04:00</updated><title> Mailchimp 首席执行官 Rania Succar 解释了为什么电子邮件公司对 Intuit 有意义</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Intuit Mailchimp 首席执行官 Rania Succar 的肖像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5Z7AFg4I31q9jlJ23BsC-y-LKY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn。 vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246692/VRG_DCD_Rania_Succar.0.jpg&quot; />;